OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers will
OL,6,Fdie out this evening. Then turning
OL,7,Fcloudier with rain spreading in from
OL,8,Fthe west during the early hours, this
OL,9,Foccasionally heavy later. Freshening
OL,10,Fwinds for Argyll.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FA cloudy morning with
OL,13,Foccasional heavy rain at first.
OL,14,FShowers will develop for the
OL,15,Fafternoon, some possibly heavy with
OL,16,Fthe odd rumble of thunder. Argyll
OL,17,Frather windy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
